data.description: Beautifully Unique One Story Home, 3 bedroom 2 bath with carport. Perfectly located in the heart of one of the most desirable areas of Coral Springs. Freshly painted inside. Updated kitchen cabinets. Stainless steel appliances. Bathrooms with contemporary tile and vanities. Enjoy outdoor entertaining in the all fenced backyard with an open patio and pretty landscaping. Close to shopping, restaurants, walking distance to Ramblewood Primary and Middle schools, parks, hospitals etc. No HOA /No Age Restrictions. No Leasing restrictions.
